content: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <rdf:RDF xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/" xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#"> <channel rdf:about="http://hdl.handle.net/2160/366"> <title>RSP Papers</title> <link>http://hdl.handle.net/2160/366</link> <description>Papers published by the RSP project</description> <items> <rdf:Seq> <rdf:li rdf:resource="http://hdl.handle.net/2160/564"/> <rdf:li rdf:resource="http://hdl.handle.net/2160/325"/> <rdf:li rdf:resource="http://hdl.handle.net/2160/312"/> <rdf:li rdf:resource="http://hdl.handle.net/2160/308"/> </rdf:Seq> </items> <dc:date>2015-03-19T06:19:34Z</dc:date> </channel> <item rdf:about="http://hdl.handle.net/2160/564"> <title>Working together for the greater good: the mutual benefits to be gained from engaging with your institutional repository project</title> <link>http://hdl.handle.net/2160/564</link> <description>Working together for the greater good: the mutual benefits to be gained from engaging with your institutional repository project Bailey, Steve; Knowles, Jackie </description> <dc:date>2008-07-01T00:00:00Z</dc:date> </item> <item rdf:about="http://hdl.handle.net/2160/325"> <title>Class of 2007: The Repositories Support Project Summer School</title> <link>http://hdl.handle.net/2160/325</link> <description>Class of 2007: The Repositories Support Project Summer School Knowles, Jackie The Repositories Support Project (RSP) is a major initiative from JISC to support the development and growth of the repositories network in the UK. With its first major event the RSP team offered 23 prospective and new repository managers from Higher Education institutions across the UK the opportunity to participate in an intensive 48-hour repository summer school. Held at the inspirational and delightful Dartington Hall in Devon, this three-day residential course delivered a comprehensive overview of the practical challenges and solutions to effective repository implementation. </description> <dc:date>2007-07-01T00:00:00Z</dc:date> </item> <item rdf:about="http://hdl.handle.net/2160/312"> <title>Repository presentations from Gregynog colloquium 2007</title> <link>http://hdl.handle.net/2160/312</link> <description>Repository presentations from Gregynog colloquium 2007 Knowles, Jackie; Lewis, Stuart; Yates, Chris; Hubbard, Bill; Bell, Anne </description> <dc:date>2007-06-26T13:14:03Z</dc:date> </item> <item rdf:about="http://hdl.handle.net/2160/308"> <title>Institutional Repositories: The New University Challenge</title> <link>http://hdl.handle.net/2160/308</link> <description>Institutional Repositories: The New University Challenge Pennock, Maureen; Lewis, Stuart </description> <dc:date>2007-04-01T00:00:00Z</dc:date> </item> </rdf:RDF>
